<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RevPay | Premier Banking & Digital Payments</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --navy: #0f172a; --gold: #eab308; --accent: #2563eb; --text: #ffffff; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--navy); color: var(--text); margin: 0; }
        
        header { padding: 30px 80px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .logo-icon { width: 35px; height: 35px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 5px; }
        
        .hero { padding: 100px 80px; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.1; }
        .hero p { font-size: 18px; color: #94a3b8; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
        
        .btn { padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
        
        .features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 40px; padding: 80px; }
        .card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo"><div class="logo-icon">R</div> RevPay</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/login" style="color:white; text-decoration:none; margin-right:20px;">Client Login</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Join RevPay</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1 style="color: var(--gold);">Global Banking, Evolved.</h1>
        <p>The secure, high-efficiency platform for personal and business wealth management. Experience institutional-grade security.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Open an Account</a>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="card"><h3>01. Security</h3><p>Military-grade AES encryption ensures your funds stay protected.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>02. Global</h3><p>Seamless international transfers with optimized exchange rates.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>03. Business</h3><p>Enterprise tools for automated invoicing and payroll management.</p></div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>